<https://city-artificial-intelligence.github.io/diso/ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A small OWL vocabulary for describing DISO (Defence, Intelligence and Security Ontologies) as a VoID / Dublin Core network of ontologies. It specialises void:Dataset into the ontology network, its subdomain clusters, and its member ontologies. Descriptive metadata reuses Dublin Core Terms and VoID terms directly." .
